CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 16, 1946, pg. 5, reads: "BIRTHDAY PARTY - William G. Calhoun of Hillcrest Street was recently honored on his fifth birthday with a gay party. Guests were Barbara Ann Crump, Allen Crump, Dale Jones, May Cooper, Barbara Fickling, Audrey Fickling, Lawrence Bagwell, Rayford West and Judith West. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: William G. Calhoun seated behind cake for his fifth birthday party, surrounded by Barbara Ann Crump, Allen Crump, Dale Jones, May Cooper, Barbara Fickling, Audrey Fickling, Lawrence Bagwell, Rayford West, Judith West, and man, in home with Washington DC commemorative pillow, Hillcrest Street
